eo, and hear updates on our media download policies."}],"kind":"article","sections":[],"references":{"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2020/10655":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10655","type":"download","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2020\/10655","checksum":null},"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"},"WWDC20-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC20-Icon.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-Icon.png"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 12, Swift 5.3, iOS 14, macOS 11 (Big Sur), tvOS 14, watchOS 7."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"code":"WidgetKit","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"StoreKit Testing","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and more."}],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20","title":"WWDC20","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","images":[{"identifier":"WWDC20-Icon.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg","type":"card"}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC18-507-AVContentKeySession-Best-Practices":{"abstract":[{"text":"AVContentKeySession allows for the management of FairPlay content decryption keys for HTTP Live Streaming. It offers a simplified key loading process that provides applications with control over the lifecycle of content keys, and features such as dual-expiry keys for offline movie rentals. Learn about best practices and recommended patterns for adopting this API.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc18-507-avcontentkeysession-best-practices","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC18-507-AVContentK